data.description:
Owner currently updating and painting to make it turn key for new buyers

Welcome to this delightful 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom home nestled in the charming small town of Borger, Texas. This home boasts a range of modern amenities and updates, making it a perfect blend of comfort and convenience.

As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting living space. The home features central heat and air, ensuring year-round comfort. The newer windows not only provide ample natural light but also enhance energy efficiency.

Located in Borger, known for its friendly community and small-town charm, this home offers a peaceful living environment while still being close to local amenities. Whether you're a first-time homebuyer or looking to downsize, this home is a fantastic opportunity
